## ChastiseMO
*Chastise Mouse Over*
#showtooltip Holy Word: Chastise
/cast [@mouseover,harm,nodead] [harm] [@mouseovertarget,harm] [@targettarget,harm] []Holy Word: Chastise

## death
*Shadowword Deatch Target*
#showtooltip
/cast [@target,harm,nodead] [@targettarget harm] Shadow Word: Death;  [] Shadow Word: Death


## Shield
*Shield target or enemy target*
#showtooltip Power Word: Shield
/cast [@target,help,nodead][@targettarget,help,nodead]Power Word: Shield; [] Power Word: Shield;

#showtooltip Smite
/cast [@mouseover,harm,nodead] [harm] [@mouseovertarget,harm] [@targettarget,harm] []Smite


/focus
/script SetRaidTargetIcon("target",4)

/script [mod:shift][@target,exists]focus; SetRaidTargetIcon("target",4); [nomod:shift] target @focus
